<chapter id="intro_admin">
  &intro_common;

  <section>
    <title>About this document</title>
    <para>
      This manual discusses installation and configuration of &ps;. Furthermore
      the system management utilities are described.
    </para>
    <para>
      For a detailed discussion of the user utilities and the programming
      interfaces included in the standard distribution take a look at the
      <ulink url="../userguide/index.html" type="dontshow">&ps; Users
	Guide</ulink> and the <ulink url="../api/index.html"
	type="dontshow">API reference</ulink> respectively.
    </para>
    <para>
      This document describes version 3.3 of the &ps3; software for Myrinet,
      version 1.0 of &psfe; and version 4.0 of &ps4;.
    </para>
  </section>
</chapter>

